column5: Died this morning at 79 years of age!  She had such beautiful eyes.
Fair lady ! Broke a few hearts too I understand
After "National Velvet" all us young lads fell in love with her...her eyes were like looking into deep pools of water...
Went out with grace, no evident plastic surgery. Why did she always pick the bad boys anyway?
Darn! Even if it doesn't last?????
